hcc_text: West Burnside Avenue is a pedestrian high crash corridor (top 10% for pedestrian deaths and serious injuries per mile in the Bronx)
info: At West Burnside Avenue at Sedgwick Avenue and West 179th Street, there were 2 deaths and severe injuries in crashes between 2008 and 2012.
